{"tid":1773146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"勿忘中亞 納粹式集中營 維族主席寄語國際聯手看待中國人權","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T14:29:37.000Z","uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a18b23042bb991f60c73f2242e87d149c6e77726","tid":1773146,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"「一年間，集中營人數由大約數十萬至百萬人，倍增至現時多達300萬人，中共政府急速擴建集中營，打壓少數民族，內裏過着的，全是非人生活。」艾沙續說，他認識一些哈薩克朋友，不幸被關在集中營8個月後獲釋，跟他說出集中營經歷。<br />\n他說：「內裏衞生環境惡劣，廁所總是排着長長人龍，要等3小時才可上廁所，不少人忍尿忍出病來。每天還要站6至7小時。食物供應不足，如早餐只有熱水和麵包，許多人整天都餓着。那位哈薩克朋友目睹至少30人被管控集中營的政府人員毆打，然後沒有再出現，究竟是死了還是重傷就醫？沒有人知道，他只知道，天天都要上課，學習自我批判，學習背誦中國國歌，承認習近平是偉大的國家領導人&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191207/60349211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60349211&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=2e9c81b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60349211&h=456359a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191207/60349211</a>"},{"pid":"647c426fc21ad231878bae91e4a21346334acea0","tid":1773146,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img 